We’ll dive straight in here and update the server using:

  # yum -y update

for completeness we’ll reboot after the update:

  # reboot

Next, we need to get wget! wget will help us download the ZPanel installation package:

  # yum install wget

Next we’ll grab the installer package from github like this:

  # wget https://rawgit.com/srapsware/zPanel/master/CentOS-6_4/10_1_1.sh
  # chmod +x 10_1_1.sh
  # sh 10_1_1.sh

next follow the instruction.

